snippet.title: 2039 Legend of Mystic Zone 聖域傳說 PC DOS 1440p 60fps
snippet.description:
You can support my channel during online streams by using the $ Superchat button. 
I cannot make any future platforms like PS1, Dreamcast, PS2, Game Cube, Xbox without cracking sound and stutterings until I upgrade my PC, so please support me.

Runplays are like movies, they're intended to show you all levels, dialogs and music, they don't show my skill. I use filters, high resolutions and hacking skills to bring you this experience. If you want a perfectly smooth 60fps experience,  use Firefox as your browser. Chrome, Vivaldi and other browsers drop a lot of frames. The best looking quality is only in 1440p, others are significantly worse. If you watch in 1080p, know that you miss a lot. Worse texture quality, worse draw distance quality etc etc.
